00:44:39.040 --> 00:44:51.040
But I will tell you that, you know, we have onboarded hundreds of customers that have had a variety of security needs and we haven't lost any deals specifically because security.

00:44:51.040 --> 00:44:58.040
So I come into support here and I do security.

00:44:58.040 --> 00:45:04.040
There's package security, security package downloads.

00:45:04.040 --> 00:45:07.040
I think this is probably a good place.

00:45:07.040 --> 00:45:10.040
So SSL, right.

00:45:10.040 --> 00:45:15.040
Cross-origin resource sharing, right.

00:45:15.040 --> 00:45:23.040
So if there's specific questions, too, I'm always happy to take that offline and help connect you with the right person internally.

00:45:23.040 --> 00:45:26.040
I'll just put my email there, too, if it's useful.

