because they do seem like SQL and Excel seems like something you'll want to,

00:51:21.040 --> 00:51:31.040
especially Excel, master that before you master R based on its use in the workplace.

00:51:31.040 --> 00:51:38.040
I think R is a niche programming language mostly used by scientists who are seeking the truth.

00:51:38.040 --> 00:51:42.040
