00:52:03.040 --> 00:52:09.040
So it's not a surprise that, like, in academia, you're using R to do science and learning,

00:52:09.040 --> 00:52:12.040
and then the industry is using more enterprise tools.

00:52:12.040 --> 00:52:14.040
