00:56:33.040 --> 00:56:37.040
I think going through the process of saying, like, you know, R,

00:56:38.040 --> 00:56:42.040
you take all the emotions out of it and say, like, you have a business to run, right?

00:56:42.040 --> 00:56:43.040
We're talking just enterprise.

